<br />
Bluescape is a visual collaboration tool designed to help people and enterprises produce their best work. It lets you interact in real time with colleagues virtually or in person with a unique set of tools that improve and streamline your existing workflows. Digital tools like note cards, pen writing, and canvases mirror traditional analog methods, while the ability to insert browser windows and web hosted content bring the internet to your fingertips.<br />
<br />
Bluescape is a cloud-based platform, so your work is available anywhere you have an internet connection and can be accessed simultaneously by other collaborators. Your team can work together in real-time regardless of location or time zone &ndash; you can collaborate on your terms.
